\"from\": 668, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"a serious hip fracture\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 711}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His coach even suggested that he go back to school.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His coach\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 745}, {\"ngram\": \"school\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, one year later, Xie won the men's 200-meter gold medal in 21.22 seconds for China at the Youth Summer Olympics in Singapore.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 873, \"end\": 878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9988242441996606, \"rank\": 0.001163278499258307, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 911, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9987900237547087, \"rank\": 0.0012106887685957247, \"text\": \"Singapore\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 816}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200-meter gold medal\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"21.22 seconds\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 868}, {\"ngram\": \"the Youth Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similar moments have continued to repeat themselves with Xie since then.\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Similar moments\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 938}, {\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He made his Olympic debut before turning 19 in London in 2012, broke the men's 200-meter domestic record and the men's 4x100-meter replay Asian record at 21 and secured the 4x100-meter silver with the best Asian performance at the World Championships in Athletics in Beijing in 2015.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1043, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.8700675532206074, \"rank\": 0.14933218996203423, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1202, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1854936684199478e-11, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999479721295, \"rank\": 5.202786533632979e-08, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200-meter domestic record\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 4x100-meter replay Asian record\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1146}, {\"ngram\": \"the 4x100-meter silver\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"Athletics\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1259}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, Xie failed to reach the men's 200-meter final at both the Asian Games in 2014 and the World Championships in 2015.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1297}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200-meter final\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1339}, {\"ngram\": \"both the Asian Games\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he set the new Chinese record for the men's 100-meter event in 9.97 seconds in 2017 and the new Asian record for the men's 200-meter race in 19.88 seconds in 2018, right before having to quit the Asian Games in 2018 due to injury.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the new Chinese record\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1443}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meter event\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"9.97 seconds\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1489}, {\"ngram\": \"the new Asian record\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 200-meter race\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"19.88 seconds\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1568}, {\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 1606, \"to\": 1621}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xie Zhenye (#6) of China competes in the men's 100-meter final at the 19th Asian Games in Hangzhou, east China's Zhejiang Province, September 30, 2023.\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1797, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Zhenye\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xie Zhenye\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Zhenye\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xie_Zhenye\"}, {\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9988242441996606, \"rank\": 0.001163278499258307, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.154776916497149e-14, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meter final\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"the 19th Asian Games\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP Xie went through similar twists at the Tokyo Olympic Games in 2021 as well.\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/College_Football_Playoff\", \"score\": 0.9999471772298488, \"rank\": 5.2823852265519475e-05, \"text\": \"CFP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/College_Football_Playoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/College_Football_Playoff\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"similar twists\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished the men's 100-meter preliminary in 10.16 seconds and failed to advance to the next stage.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10.16 seconds\", \"from\": 1927, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the next stage\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, later he became the first Chinese sprinter to reach the men's 200-meter semifinals at the Olympics in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 1982, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9927116248797171, \"rank\": 0.007337116549785857, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2093, \"end\": 2098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9993974961971726, \"rank\": 0.0006028127189452224, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's 200-meter semifinals\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xie found encouragement from his teammate Su Bingtian, who made the men's 100-meter final in 9.83 seconds.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Bingtian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Su Bingtian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Bingtian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Su_Bingtian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"encouragement\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meter final\", \"from\": 2165, \"to\": 2190}, {\"ngram\": \"9.83 seconds\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2206}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not run well in my race, but hearing the exciting news of my teammate was great encouragement and improvement of my confidence,\\\" Xie told China media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 2373, \"end\": 2376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"score\": 0.8113220709341218, \"rank\": 0.19860304936680434, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my race\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"the exciting news\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"my teammate\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2285}, {\"ngram\": \"great encouragement\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"improvement\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"my confidence\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At that moment I knew someone else could do it, which gave me confidence to stick to what I do.\\\"\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2394}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xie decided to change his running style after the Tokyo Olympics and it wasn't easy, especially for an athlete in his age.\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"his running style\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 2578, \"to\": 2588}, {\"ngram\": \"his age\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, he did it and won his first Asian Games individual gold medal by finishing the men's 100-meter event in 9.97 seconds in Hangzhou, east China's Zhejiang Province, in 2023.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2642, \"end\": 2647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1854936684199478e-11, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2734, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.154776916497149e-14, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the men's 100-meter event\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2714}, {\"ngram\": \"9.97 seconds\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think the Asian Games is a period to me.\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2810}, {\"ngram\": \"a period\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not perfect, but it's an end,\\\" Xie told CMG.\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2875, \"end\": 2878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"score\": 0.8113220709341218, \"rank\": 0.19860304936680434, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yo_Gotti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an end\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2863}, {\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's more than realizing an Asian Games dream.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999881766, \"rank\": 1.1854936684199478e-11, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In my career, I have participated in the Asian Games, the Olympics, the World Championships among other domestic and international tournaments and I have accomplished something.\\\"\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2931, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 2980}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"other domestic and international tournaments\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In my age now, I think it's a process to let many things go,\\\" Xie added.\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3181, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my age\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3118}, {\"ngram\": \"a process\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"many things\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"Xie\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I used to work hard for the results, but now that the period is written, I just want to enjoy and display the process.\\\"\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the results\", \"from\": 3207, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"the period\", \"from\": 3233, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466 SITEMAP EXPLORE MORE DOWNLOAD OUR APP Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7 Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SITEMAP\", \"from\": 3304, \"to\": 3311}, {\"ngram\": \"MORE DOWNLOAD\", \"from\": 3320, \"to\": 3333}, {\"ngram\": \"Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\", \"from\": 3342, \"to\": 3384}, {\"ngram\": \"Disinformation report hotline\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3415}, {\"ngr